499
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:25,160
 potrebujem matić,

500
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:25,340
 ali,

501
00:24:25,340 --> 00:24:25,900
 Bože,

502
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:27,260
 da li je to tvoja svjeta volja?

503
00:24:27,260 --> 00:24:29,000
 I razmišljala sam,

504
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:29,620
 promišljala,

505
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:30,800
 prikazivala i sve,

506
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:33,640
 i dobivala sam ja od nekih

507
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,980
 izdavačkih kuća,

508
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:36,400
 kako su neki znali,

509
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:36,580
 evo,

510
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,120
 da pišem,

511
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:37,920
 pa da prekidem,

512
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:38,220
 pa to,

513
00:24:38,220 --> 00:24:39,160
 pa hoćeš,

514
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:39,500
 ono,

515
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:41,640
 da započnemo neku suradnju,

516
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,120
 sve to meni ništa,

517
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:44,320
 njeno zazvonila,

518
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:47,840
 i onda se javi vjerbu,

519
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:48,900
 jednostavno,

520
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:49,940
 to je bilo baš odgovor,

521
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:50,940
 to je to,

522
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:51,920
 idem,

523
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,900
 idemo dalje,

524
00:24:52,900 --> 00:24:54,060
 i gospodine,

525
00:24:54,060 --> 00:24:54,780
 svoja milošća,

526
00:24:54,780 --> 00:24:55,420
