553
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,440
 duhom tješiteljem,

554
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:38,080
 duhom Božem istine,

555
00:25:38,080 --> 00:25:40,780
 da se tamo ne raskrinka,

556
00:25:40,780 --> 00:25:42,100
 baš je bila ta borba,

