613
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:19,860
 nisam znala uopće što se dogodilo s menom,

614
00:27:19,860 --> 00:27:21,800
 tko se to je iživljavao nad menom,

615
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:23,800
 a samo sam jedno htjela doći doma,

616
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:24,380
 doći doma,

617
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:26,860
 staviti se po tu moju dekicu,

618
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,800
 skloniti se po tu moju dekicu

619
00:27:28,800 --> 00:27:30,680
 i jednostavno da se obranim,

620
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:33,220
 da stavim neki štica tom svojom dekicom

621
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,160
 na sebe,

622
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:36,340
 ali onda kad dođeš na tabor

623
00:27:36,340 --> 00:27:39,540
 i onda kad zaplovioš u tu dubine,

624
00:27:39,540 --> 00:27:41,560
 dubine s gospodinom,

625
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:42,880
 dubine duhovnog svijeta,

626
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,940
 onda počinješ biti cjestan,

627
00:27:44,940 --> 00:27:47,360
