630
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,260
 a to je satona,

631
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:56,800
 to nije čovjek ko je i slap, i grešan, i ranjen, i zerugljen.

632
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,260
 Ja znam s kojim imam borbu,

633
00:27:58,260 --> 00:28:00,480
 znači nemam borbu sa niti ljudima,

634
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:02,480
 niti Hrvatima, niti Njemcima,

635
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:05,180
 niti Englezima, niti onom...

636
00:28:05,180 --> 00:28:06,880
 nacijom.

637
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:09,440
 Ja nemam niti ras, znači ja se ne borim s čovjekom.

638
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,120
 Ja znam

639
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:13,180
 čija je moja borba, protiv koga se borim,

640
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:14,520
 ali Bogu hvala,

641
00:28:14,520 --> 00:28:17,000
 Bog je jači od svakog zlajka,

642
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,060
 kao što kaže sveti Mihajl,

643
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:19,300
