655
00:28:50,660 --> 00:28:52,160
 koji te na kraju toliko zaposljio,

656
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:54,000
 da si ti zapravo godinama išla

657
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:58,140
 idući, odnosno na Euharistiju,

658
00:28:58,140 --> 00:28:59,140
 da življavala te manifestacije,

659
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:02,040
 na kraju išla čak i koliko mjeseci.

660
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:04,360
 11 mjeseci na egzorcizam.

661
00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:06,140
 Znači to je bilo jedno zaposljednuće

662
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:08,340
 na jednoj visokoj razini,

663
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:12,400
 odnosno čvrsto te se dohvatilo.

664
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,060
 Što ti misliš?

665
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:15,660
 Pa nije to moglo možda zbog, ne znam,

666
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:17,040
 krivog društva ili je,

667
00:29:17,040 --> 00:29:21,540
 ili je zbog možda odlazaka kod vidovnjakinje?

668
00:29:21,540 --> 00:29:22,060
 Što misliš?

669
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:23,360
 Ili je to skup svega?

670
00:29:23,360 --> 00:29:26,280
 Kako si došla do toga tako mlada?

671
00:29:26,280 --> 00:29:27,180
 Pa mlada.

672
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:31,440
 Prvi greh koji se otisnio u mene je bio taj greh zlostavljena.

673
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:33,740
 Ja sam bila seksualno zlostavljena

674
00:29:33,740 --> 00:29:36,400
 što sam u jednom dijelom knjigu makla iz knjige.

675
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:39,180
 nisam htjela taj dio detaljirati o toj osobi.

676
00:29:39,180 --> 00:29:41,220
 Ja sam toj osobi oprostila

677
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:43,380
 i molim se za tu osobu

678
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:46,040
 i zaista moje srce je u miru prema toj osobi.

679
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,960
 Ima svakoj osobi

680
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,800
 koja je išta očinila

681
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:51,780
 prema meni, prema moj srcu,

682
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:52,720
 prema mome tijelu.

683
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:55,980
 jer znam, moj Isus je oprostio meni

684
00:29:55,980 --> 00:29:57,660
 i kako ja da ne prostim onima

685
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,420
 koji ga ne poznaju,

686
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,840
 koji ga još nisu poznali,

687
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:01,980
 jer da su ga opoznali,

688
00:30:01,980 --> 00:30:05,120
 konačnici ne bi činili to pre meni što su činili.

689
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,220
 sve to, znači,

690
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:10,140
 Patraz jedan često govorio,

691
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:12,080
 ne pretrat čovjeka su svijet, tijelo i džavo.

692
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:13,320
 Svijet koji nas vuče se,

693
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:15,540
 svijet koji ima svoje propagande.

694
00:30:15,540 --> 00:30:18,180
 Onda tu je tijelo koje je puno požude,

695
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:19,580
 a onda tu je džavo

696
00:30:19,580 --> 00:30:21,640
 koji te vabi

697
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,840
 kroz različite,

698
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:24,600
 evo, astrologija, horoskop,

699
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:25,940
 fidovnjaci, hođe,

700
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,400
 sve to gdje sam ja

701
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:30,040
 sa svojim koracijima išla.

702
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:32,400
 Ali naravno,

703
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:35,000
 da bi džavo opće došlo do čovjeka,

704
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,880
 djelovao kroz čovjeka,

705
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,600
 potreba da čovjek bude ranjen.

706
00:30:38,600 --> 00:30:40,020
 Jer on kroz ranu ulazi.

707
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:42,240
 Ja sam prvenstvo bila ranjena

708
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,940
 kad me prvi put moja majka ostavila.

709
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:46,020
 Bila sam malena djevojčica

710
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:47,400
 koja je mama bila sve.

711
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,640
 Ja sam znači sve imala uzor u svojom majci

712
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,840
 i kasnije kad se ona me ni vratila u život

713
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:54,560
 ja sam mu na jedan nezrav način kupovala.

714
00:30:54,560 --> 00:30:57,060
 Poklonima, kupovala sam je pažnjom.

715
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:59,340
 Kupovala sam je time

716
00:30:59,340 --> 00:31:00,760
 da joj ne iznosim neke stvari,

717
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:02,640
 da ona ne bude povrijeđena time.

718
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,900
 Samo da bi imala svoju majku blizu.

719
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,100
 A to je ono što danas

720
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:07,160
 mnogo djeca čine.

721
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,240
 Žele privući pažnju roditelja,

722
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,820
 žele kupiti svoje roditele,

723
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:12,940
 njihovu pažnju, njihovu ljubav,

724
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:15,060
 a pritom sakreti

725
00:31:15,060 --> 00:31:16,480
 onu stvarnost

726
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,140
 u kojem se oni zaista nalaze.

727
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:20,980
 Zapravo spomenula sam malo prije ovo

728
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:23,620
 jer više puta navodiš

729
00:31:23,620 --> 00:31:24,880
 i čitanje horoskopa

730
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:26,480
 i odlazak kod vidovnjakinje.

731
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,280
 Misli da se to premalo

732
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:30,300
 naglašava koliko je to

733
00:31:30,300 --> 00:31:31,180
 izvor

734
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:34,460
 izvor zla zapravo,

735
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:35,500
 ali možemo reći.

736
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:38,040
 A možemo pročitati tu

737
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:39,520
 svakodnevnim časopisima,

738
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:41,900
 svaki dan na televiziji.

739
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:43,880
 ti možeš posvjedočiti da je to

740
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,800
 zapravo nije mala šala.

741
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:46,720
 Nije mala šala.

742
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:47,200
 Uostalom,

743
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,520
 to je otac laži.

744
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:51,220
 I šta otac laži ti nudi u horoskopu?

745
00:31:51,220 --> 00:31:52,820
 Da otkriješ kako će ti biti ljubav?

746
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:53,400
 A koja je ljubav?

747
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,120
 Boga je ljubav.

748
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:56,180
 Otkrivati zdravlja.

749
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,640
 Što ti vredi zdravo tijelo

750
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:59,340
 ako ti je zluh slab

751
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:00,440
 ili duh zarobljen.

752
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,980
 Konačno si nuditi

753
00:32:01,980 --> 00:32:03,400
 tu jednu lažnu

754
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:05,720
 lažnu nadu

755
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:08,160
 i prikazanje novac,

756
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,100
 posao.

757
00:32:09,100 --> 00:32:10,360
 Bože,

758
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:11,800
 ako si ti meni rekao

759
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:13,180
 da se ne brinem tijeskobno,

760
00:32:13,180 --> 00:32:14,560
 hraniš ptice na grani,

761
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:15,900
 polsko cijeće oblačeć,

762
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:17,560
 zašto da se brinem tijeskobno,

763
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:18,800
 to će meni zloduh

764
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,440
 prorokovati

765
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,980
 na lažan način

766
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:23,340
 da pročitam

767
00:32:23,340 --> 00:32:25,560
 oću li ja ima sljedeći mjesec novaca ili ne.

768
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:25,980
 Mislim,

769
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:28,660
 pa ako nam je svaka vlasna glavi zbrana,

770
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:30,740
 nijedna neopada bez očeva znanja,

771
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:32,360
 pa neće joj vjerojat tamo

772
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:33,560
 jednom horoskopu.

773
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,780
 Ja vjerujem živo me Bogu,

774
00:32:35,780 --> 00:32:36,920
 a se njegovo dijete.

775
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,300
 A što je njegova volja?

776
00:32:38,300 --> 00:32:39,540
 Da život imamo.

777
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:40,400
 A kako?

778
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,860
 Da mu budemo vjerni,

779
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:42,680
 da ga slijedimo,

780
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:44,460
 da vršimo njegove zapovjedi,

781
00:32:44,460 --> 00:32:45,960
 a iznad svega da ga ljubimo,

782
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,480
 njega i bližnjega

783
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,480
 ko samoga sebe.

784
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:52,480
 Da, mislim da tu ono manjak povjerenja.

785
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:53,640
 Ja znam po sebi, evo,

786
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:55,860
 trudim se sve više,

787
00:32:56,480 --> 00:33:00,480
 puštati tu kontrolu.

788
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:03,020
 Mi ljudi bismo htjeli imati neku kontrolu,

789
00:33:03,020 --> 00:33:03,840
 nekakvu

790
00:33:03,840 --> 00:33:06,760
 potpisanu,

791
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:09,140
 ono, potpisano što će se dogoditi.

792
00:33:09,140 --> 00:33:10,900
 Čisto da mi sebe zaštitimo,

793
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:12,300
 potencijalnih nekih,

794
00:33:12,300 --> 00:33:15,200
 možda, povrijeđenosti i tako dalje.

795
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,420
 I onda to povjerenje,

796
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:18,720
 da ne moram znati,

797
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:20,580
 ne trebam znati što me čeka sutra,

798
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:22,100
 ali nama ljudima,

799
00:33:22,100 --> 00:33:22,820
 evo ja prvo...

800
00:33:22,820 --> 00:33:24,040
 Svi smo radoznali.

801
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:25,280
 Da, svi smo radoznali

802
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:27,740
 i želimo kontrolirati situaciju.

803
00:33:27,820 --> 00:33:29,840
 E, ali to ti sve zajedno,

804
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:30,700
 radoznalost,

805
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:31,880
 kontrola

806
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,320
 i nestrpljivost.

807
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:33,640
 Da.

808
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:34,940
 A to sve voditi jedno s drugim.

809
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:36,660
 Ljudi često su nestrpljivi,

810
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:38,440
 radoznali što će biti

811
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,240
 i htjeli bi imati sve pod kontrolom.

812
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,740
 To su sve sestrice.

813
00:33:41,740 --> 00:33:44,460
 Isti kruk koji veže jedan s drugim.

814
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:46,360
 Zato treba se toga osloboditi

815
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:48,700
 i samo tražiti Bože kraljestvo

816
00:33:48,700 --> 00:33:49,580
 i pravdu u njegovu.

817
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:50,540
 I to svakodnevno.

818
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:51,780
 Umirati sebe,

819
00:33:51,780 --> 00:33:53,200
 derovati se za njega

820
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:55,280
 i u konačnosti ljubiti bližnjega.

821
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:56,240
 Jel'i...

822
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,240
 Gdje je moja plaća?

823
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,300
 Tu, među bližnjima.

824
00:33:58,300 --> 00:33:59,120
 Gdje je među onima

825
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,280
 i koji mene proganjaju,

826
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:01,820
 koji mene razumiju,

827
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:03,820
 koji me kleveću,

828
00:34:03,820 --> 00:34:05,060
 koji me ismijavanju.

829
00:34:05,060 --> 00:34:05,540
 Pa Bože,

830
00:34:05,540 --> 00:34:08,440
 ja im neću uzvraćati njihov način.

831
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,980
 Ne zašto što možda oni,

832
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:11,460
 možda njegi njeni ne ubodu.

833
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:14,340
 Nego zato što si me ti pozvao

834
00:34:14,340 --> 00:34:15,240
 na ljubav.

835
00:34:15,240 --> 00:34:17,320
 I ako sam ja shvatila

836
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,500
 Boži poziv,

837
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,780
 šta je ljubav?

838
00:34:19,780 --> 00:34:22,220
 Onda znam da neću uzvraćati mirom

839
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,580
 koji oni me mjere

840
00:34:23,580 --> 00:34:25,660
 ili sudom koji me oni sude.

841
00:34:25,660 --> 00:34:27,740
 Jel'i se nekad osjetiš usamljena

842
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:30,360
 na toj razini duhovnosti?

843
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,520
 Jel' ti teško pronaći

844
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:33,520
 prijateljice koje te razumiju?

845
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:36,200
 Ne, ja Bogu hvala imam i prijateljice.

846
00:34:36,200 --> 00:34:37,620
 Tu su i moje kume

847
00:34:37,620 --> 00:34:39,760
 i kuma kata

848
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,340
 koja mi je duhovna majka,

849
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:42,780
 tu časna sestra Matija Pavić,

850
00:34:42,780 --> 00:34:43,420
 poglavarica,

851
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:45,100
 krenateljica Krvi Kristovi,

852
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:45,780
 svećenici,

853
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:47,540
 moji duhovni oci koji me prate,

854
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:48,200
 moj duhovnik,

855
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:48,980
 fraj Ivan Matić.

856
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,760
 Ja zaista imam veliku milost,

857
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,400
 moje srce ima veliku milost

858
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:55,420
 da imam predivne ljude

859
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,800
 u mom životu,

860
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:57,540
 ne oko mene,

861
00:34:57,540 --> 00:34:59,080
 nego u mome životu,

862
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:00,100
 u mome srcu,

863
00:35:00,100 --> 00:35:01,260
 savjetima,

864
00:35:01,260 --> 00:35:01,940
 ljubavlju,

865
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:02,820
 brigom,

866
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:04,020
 milosrđem,

867
00:35:04,020 --> 00:35:05,360
 opomenom,

868
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,280
 ukorom,

869
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:08,040
 tješenjem,

870
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,300
 utjehom i svemu.

871
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,940
 Zaista i to je veliki dar

872
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:12,820
 i na tobe ne prostano zahvalju.

873
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:18,700
 Jel ti nekad bude ono osjećaj kao da želiš spasiti neke ljude iz svoje prošlosti?

874
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:19,180
 Naravno.

875
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:21,220
 Prije nego što nastavimo s razgovorom,

876
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:25,380
 samo mali podsjetnik da današnju epizodu ponosno sponsorira like,

877
00:35:25,380 --> 00:35:28,580
 hrvatski brand personaliziranog predivnog nakita.

878
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:30,860
 Njihovi komadi nisu samo ukrasne,

879
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:36,040
 nego dolaze sa mirisnim medaljonima koji subtilno odpuštaju parfem ili eterično ulje kroz dan.

880
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,980
 Svaki komad možeš personalizirati gravurom,

881
00:35:38,980 --> 00:35:42,560
 odabrati motiv i boju pozlate,

882
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:46,460
 tako da je like savršen kao pokloni ili mala uspomena za sebe.

883
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:49,580
 Izrađeni su od kvalitetnih hipoalergenih materijala,

884
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:51,220
 pa su ugodni za nositi svaki dan.

885
00:35:51,220 --> 00:35:53,180
 Ako želiš vidjeti sve uživo,

886
00:35:53,180 --> 00:35:56,200
 posjeti njihov predivni showroom u Zagrebu,

887
00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:59,700
 a naravno da sve možeš vidjeti i na njihovoj web trgovini.

888
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:02,060
 A sedajmo nazad na razgovor.

889
00:36:02,060 --> 00:36:05,500
 Naravno, problemstveno ljudi iz moje obitelji

890
00:36:05,500 --> 00:36:10,380
 i bilo mi teško i stvarno sad bih ja cupkala za rukav.

891
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:12,560
 Ajde, dođi, dođi na izvor, dođi Isusu.

892
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:15,140
 Ali to je to što je Boga silan i nasilan.

893
00:36:15,140 --> 00:36:18,160
 Nikog ne možemo na silu dovodi gospodinu, nikog.

894
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:20,000
 Možemo mu posvjedočiti,

895
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:23,320
 a na osobi da će mu biti otvoreno srce

896
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,540
 i oće li ona primiti to svjedočanstvo.

897
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:27,340
 I u redu je ako ne primi,

898
00:36:27,340 --> 00:36:29,800
 ako je još zatvorena iz nekih svojih rana,

899
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,360
 pobuna, zarobljenosti.

900
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,380
 Sve je to normalno, sve je to u redu.

901
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:36,280
 Ne treba gledati, aha, ako neko nije otvoren za svjedočanstvo,

902
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:38,240
 neko nije otvoren evo za osobu koja

903
00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:40,200
 se to prvobitno obratila.

904
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:42,800
 Ja kažem, zato je obročenje proces koji traje cijeli život.

905
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,280
 Znači, sve je to u redu.

906
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,560
 To prihvaćanje u redu, prihvaćam te, sestro.

907
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,580
 Ti ne razumiješ moj put,

908
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:50,340
 ne razumiješ dar vjere

909
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:52,700
 koju se moj srce trudi živjet,

